@startuml
title Search Trails

actor User
boundary SearchPanel
control TrailService
database Database

User -> SearchPanel : enterSearchCriteria(criteria)
User -> SearchPanel : clickSearch()

SearchPanel -> TrailService : searchTrails(criteria)
TrailService -> Database : findTrails(criteria)
Database --> TrailService : matchingTrails
TrailService --> SearchPanel : matchingTrails

SearchPanel --> User : displaySearchResults(matchingTrails)

@enduml
